headline: Fifth Third Bank to Decrease Prime Lending Rate to 6.75%
summary: CINCINNATI, December 10, 2025--Fifth Third Bank, National Association (Nasdaq: FITB) today announced it will decrease its prime lending rate to 6.75%, effective immediately.

headline: Fifth Third Set to Expand Multifamily Lending With Fannie Mae DUS Deal
summary: FITB agrees to acquire Mechanics Bank's DUS business, gaining a $1.8B servicing portfolio as it broadens its multifamily lending reach.

headline: Fifth Third Partners With Brex, Unlocks $5.6B Commercial Card Volume
